nted fixed-point band + the normal is unit + A->B (translating B by depth*normal makes the pair non-overlapping per a re-query of gjk::Gjk). NO hull world step/manifold (GJ4), NO lockstep (GJ5), NO lit render (GJ6), NO new RHI; gjk.h is APPEND-ONLY (GJ1+GJ2's code byte-frozen), the ONLY new shader is gjk_epa.comp (int64, Vulkan-only); convex.h/fric.h/persist.h/fpx.h + all existing sim headers + shaders + goldens UNCHANGED. CAVEATS: convex polyhedra only; EPA termination is within-band — a deterministic depth/normal, NOT guaranteed analytically optimal, the honest EPA caveat; though gjk::Epa itself is byte-identical CPU/GPU)
